HEADWORD: Chilly
<hw>Chill"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Moderately cold; cold
and raw or damp so as to cause shivering; causing or feeling a
disagreeable sensation of cold, or a shivering.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Chilognath</ent>⟦br⟧
